description: The Asus Gaming V16 is an affordable gaming laptop that offers a balance of battery life and mid-range gaming performance thanks to the Intel Core Series 2 chipsets and Nvidia GeForce RTX 4050 laptop GPU. The laptop has a minimalist design, but offers a 16-inch display and a large trackpad. Should you buy this over other similarly priced gaming laptops? Read our review to find out.
title: Asus Gaming V16 Review: Strong Battery, Mid-Range Performance
